Package com.ntu.scse

Class Bill

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ntu.scse.Bill
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Bill>

    public class Bill
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Bill>
    Represents a hotel Bill object that contains the hotel room price as well as the room service orders for that room. One BillManager can contain many Bills.
    Since:
    19/04/2018
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Cai LingZhi, Liu Fangbing, Christopher Lim, Eliza Wong

        Creates a new Bill with the given ID, reservation details, room details. Calculates the running total price as the number of nights * the price per night
        Parameters:
        billNo - This Bill's unique identifier.
        resvNo - The Reservation number associated with this bill.
        roomDays - The number of nights of stay.
        roomType - The room type associated with this bill.
        roomNo - The room number associated with this bill.
        roomRate - The room price per night associated with this bill.
        discount - The discount associated with this bill.
